### Download
You can download this project in either
[zip](https://github.com/corerd/CRDTextView/zipball/master)
or [tar](https://github.com/corerd/CRDTextView/tarball/master) formats.

You can also clone the project with
[Git](https://github.com/corerd/CRDTextView)
by running:
```
$ git clone https://github.com/corerd/CRDTextView.git
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
